data.text:
Description

Peanut Gud Gajak is known as peanut Gajak is a delicious, sweet and energy-filled bar which prepared with ingredients – Peanut, Jaggery, Sugar & Liquid Glucose and edible oils.

Gur Peanut Gajak (moofali ki Gajak) is a yummy combination of nutritious components Peanut and gud. It is good for health because of iron in jaggery and Peanuts that is rich in calcium & protein that helps to get lowering cholesterol levels. It contains no artificial flavors.

Peanut Gajak or moongfali Gajak generally made on kite festival or Makar-Sankranti festival. Peanut and jaggery both provide energy and nourishment in the body to keep the body warm during winter days .

Carry these crackers or Gajak in you bags and pop it in your mouth for an instant energy boost. Go ahead and try this product from ratlami tadka along with Ratlami Tadka Namkeen Mixture.

This is a Vegetarian Product.

Contains Gud, Peanut (moongfali) , Sugar .

Shelf life is 60 days.

Store at room temperature in an air-tight container.
